race.comment: HORRIBLE HANK (7) returned in good order with a fast-finishing win at Toowoomba and the extra furlong here looks to suit. Can make his presence felt. COMMAND APPROVED (3) was a touch disappointing last time out but the form prior was full of merit. Can bounce right back without surprising. MISHANI STELLER (13) was well fancied last time when she broke through for a maiden win over 1200m at Stanthorpe. Worth including in this lineup. BORN FEARLESS (6) has been in the market at his last couple of starts but hasn't made an impression, last start running fifth at Stanthorpe. Rates a strong each-way chance.
